    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077690/extras/a1e7ff59d62966458922c36f3e9802cf.avif?t=1747840955\" width=612 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Serial Victims is a 3D psychological horror game that immerses you in the nightmares of individuals who fell prey to serial killers. In Serial Victims, you embody each victim, racing against time to uncover clues, call for help, and perform various actions before the inevitable happens. Your ultimate objective is to have the victims assist in catching the killer with as few victims as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival is not the goal. Instead, your aim is to do what you can within the time you have left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077690/extras/d47c7887117c6c2c298b49ce597eb617.poster.avif?t=1747840955\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077690/extras/d47c7887117c6c2c298b49ce597eb617.webm?t=1747840955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077690/extras/d47c7887117c6c2c298b49ce597eb617.mp4?t=1747840955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077690/extras/534871e26d8b81b55aa5d48c49791561.avif?t=1747840955\" width=612 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Serial Victims gives a fresh and replayable horror experience. Each playthrough is randomized, ensuring that no two experiences are the same:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique players: Each victim is different, their name, speed, and reactions to their surroundings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Killers: Encounter various serial killers, each with distinct methods, personalities, and motives, making each investigation a unique challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive Experience: Realistic graphics and sounds, combined with a minimal user interface, ensure a completely immersive experience that will keep you on edge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Locations: Explore over 5 different crime scenes, each with unique twists, hiding spots, and layouts.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077690/extras/398eb0e08f2eea3f492d6c2963a767d4.poster.avif?t=1747840955\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077690/extras/398eb0e08f2eea3f492d6c2963a767d4.webm?t=1747840955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077690/extras/398eb0e08f2eea3f492d6c2963a767d4.mp4?t=1747840955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
